Welcome, Moderna! The first batch of Moderna vaccines came in this afternoon via SQ7137, from Brussels, Belgium.

@singaporeair and #SATS have been busy with cargo deliveries. This has put to good use our capabilities to handle temperature-sensitive pharmaceuticals and the connectivity with cities around the world. 

This also means we are ready to ramp up vaccination for Singaporeans.

