Woodlands Galaxy Community Centre has been designated as a COVID-19 vaccination centre. Yesterday was day 1, with 200 vaccinations for frontline workers. 

@pohlisan , who is MP and grassroots adviser in the area, visited the CC. Together with her grassroots leaders, she will soon be reaching out to the seniors to ensure that they too get vaccinated! 

